arStrings.szText: Ayuzhan asked me to find his colleague, Zoltun Kulle. Ayuzhan says we can find him in the Library, but I have my doubts.

Ayuzhan asked me to find his colleague, Zoltun Kulle. Ayuzhan says we can find him in the Library, but I have my doubts.
Zoltun Kulle is nowhere to be found. Perhaps he left a message to Ayuzhan? I should search Zoltun's Study for clues.
Before Ayuzhan and I could return to the Gatehall, the demon intervened. It appears to have some power over the old mage. I need to protect Ayuzhan from constructs while he regains control.

Before Ayuzhan and I could return to the Gatehall, the demon—Malphas— intervened. It appears to have some power over the old mage. 

I need to protect Ayuzhan from constructs while he regains control.

Before Ayuzhan and I could return to the Gatehall, the demonic voice found us. It appears to have some power over the old mage. I hope defeating the hostile constructs prevents Ayuzhan from becoming possessed once more.
The constructs are defeated and Ayuzhan possesses his own mind. We need to return to the Gatehall before Malphas returns again.
The letter revealed the truth: Kulle abandoned Ayuzhan. So be it. We'll fight the demon on our own. I should return to the Gatehall and discuss our options with Ayuzhan.
